query_water_surface_light

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_water_surface_light -  This function returns the amount of light that will filter down to rooms below this one that have had set_use_surface_light called in them.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_water_surface_light()
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the amount of light that filters down to rooms below this one.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/basic/water.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function returns the amount of light that will filter down to rooms
below this one that have had set_use_surface_light called in them.  Its
default is to return a value based on the light in this room and the clarity
of the water.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_use_surface_light, set_turbidity, set_clarity

.EP

